# human-compound CODEOWNERS
#
# Auto-assigns reviewers based on artifact type.
# Without branch protection requiring reviews, this only assigns -- it does not block merges.
#
# CUSTOMIZE: Replace placeholder teams/usernames with your own.
# Examples:
#   @your-org/team       -> @myorg/engineering  (or @alice @bob @carol)
#   @your-org/tech-lead  -> @alice
#   @your-org/engineers  -> @bob @carol

# Requirements and ideation -- whole team sees these
docs/brainstorms/       @your-org/team
docs/ideation/          @your-org/team

# Plans -- tech lead reviews
docs/plans/             @your-org/tech-lead

# Learnings -- whole team sees these
docs/solutions/         @your-org/team

# Source code -- engineers review
src/                    @your-org/engineers
app/                    @your-org/engineers
lib/                    @your-org/engineers
test/                   @your-org/engineers
tests/                  @your-org/engineers
spec/                   @your-org/engineers

# Workflow and CI config -- tech lead reviews
.github/                @your-org/tech-lead

# Fallback -- whole team
*                       @your-org/team
